<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<style>
.tooltip {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
}

.tooltip .tooltiptext {
    visibility: hidden;
    width: 120px;
    background-color: black;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 5px 0;
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 1;
    bottom: 100%;
    left:150%;
    margin-left: -60px;

    
    /* Fade in tooltip - takes 1 second to go from 0% to 100% opac: */
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1s;
}

.tooltip:hover .tooltiptext {
    visibility: visible;
    opacity: 1;
}
</style>
<body style="text-align:center;">

<h2>Fade In Tooltip on Hover</h2>
<p>When you move the mouse over the text below, the tooltip text will fade in and take 1 second to go from completely invisible to visible.</p>

<div class="tooltip">Hover over me
  <span class="tooltiptext">Tooltip text<br> Tooltip text3<br> Tooltip text7</span>
</div>

